---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Beginner Guides — Learn Scrabble From Scratch"
  description="Complete collection of beginner Scrabble guides. Learn the rules, scoring, strategy, and etiquette. Free guides with no signup required."
  keywords="scrabble beginner guide, learn scrabble, scrabble rules, how to play scrabble, scrabble tips for beginners, scrabble scoring, free scrabble guide"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What should a beginner learn first in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Start with the basic rules and board layout, then learn tile values and how scoring works. Once you understand the mechanics, move on to premium squares and simple two-letter words to build your confidence." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How long does it take to get good at Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most players see noticeable improvement within a few weeks of regular play. Learning the two-letter words and basic tile management can boost your score by 50-100 points per game almost immediately." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do I need to memorise the entire Scrabble dictionary?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "No. Knowing just the 127 two-letter words and a handful of high-value short words gives beginners a major advantage. Focus on playable words rather than obscure ones." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-1">
      <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
      <span class="mx-1">›</span>
      <span class="text-gray-300">Beginner Guides</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Beginner Guides</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
      New to Scrabble? Start here. These 10 guides cover everything from the basic rules to winning strategy, 
      scoring mechanics, and table etiquette. Each article is written for players who are just getting started 
      — no jargon, no assumptions, just clear explanations to help you play with confidence.
    </p>

    <!-- Post grid -->
    <div class="grid gap-4">
      <a href="/blog/what-is-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">What Is Scrabble?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">An introduction to the world's most popular word game — what it is, who plays it, and why it endures.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/how-to-play-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">How to Play Scrabble</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Step-by-step walkthrough of your first game — setup, turns, tile draws, and how to finish.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/scrabble-rules-explained" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Rules Explained</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Every official rule covered clearly — challenges, exchanges, timing, and what counts as a valid word.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/scrabble-scoring-guide" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Scoring Guide</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">How points are calculated — tile values, premium squares, bingo bonuses, and end-game deductions.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/understanding-premium-squares" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Understanding Premium Squares</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Double letter, triple word, and everything in between — how to use the board's bonus squares effectively.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/how-blank-tiles-work" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">How Blank Tiles Work</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The most powerful tiles in the bag — when to use them, when to save them, and the rules around blanks.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/beginner-scrabble-strategy" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Beginner Scrabble Strategy: 10 Tips</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Simple, actionable tactics that immediately improve your game — rack balance, board position, and tile management.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/common-scrabble-mistakes" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Common Mistakes New Players Make</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The most frequent errors beginners make and how to avoid them — from rack hoarding to ignoring the board.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/how-to-win-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">How to Win More Scrabble Games</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Practical winning habits — opening play, mid-game control, endgame counting, and when to exchange tiles.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/scrabble-etiquette" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Etiquette</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Unwritten rules of good sportsmanship — challenges, clock management, and how to be a gracious opponent.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Links to other category pages -->
    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">More Categories</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/two-letter-words" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Two-Letter Words — Master the 127 essential short words</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">All Blog Posts — Browse the full article archive</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA box -->
    <div class="mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-indigo-900/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">
          🔍 Practice what you've learned with our free word finder
        </p>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm"
        >
          Open Word Finder →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
